The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Coach wants discipline 
                                                                                                                       7                                      Coach wants discipline 
                      
	Johannesburg: Corrie van Zyl is an interim appointment but the new South Africa coach is excited all the same about his job and it appears that he is already working on ideas and strategies for the teams improvement.         
	First up is method and the coach says he wants to instil discipline in the side who head for India on Saturday for the Test and ODI series. I believe in team culture. The team must look after discipline and if they cant it becomes my responsibility. I will not pass the buck on that, Van Zyl said.(PTI)                                                                                                                     
